    "category": "p2e global",
    "tags": ["p2eglobal", "website", "link", "links"]
  },
  {
    "id": "13",
    "text": "The game currency of GalaxyTap is Galaxy points (GP).",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["currency", "game currency", "game"]
  },
  {
    "id": "14",
    "text": "GalaxyTap features nine stations classified by development tier: Nexus (1), Pulsar (2), Nebula (3), Eclipse (4), Aurora (5), Starlight (6), Voyager (7), Zenith (8), Endurance (9).",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["station", "stations", "tiers", "tier"]
  },
  {
    "id": "15",
    "text": "GalaxyTap features nine battleships classified by development tier: Nexus (1), Pulsar (2), Nebula (3), Eclipse (4), Aurora (5), Starlight (6), Voyager (7), Zenith (8), Endurance (9).",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["battleship", "battleships", "tiers", "tier"]
  },
  {
    "id": "16",
    "text": "Station development tier determines the auto-recovery rate and limit of station energy.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["station", "stations", "energy"]
  },
  {
    "id": "17",
    "text": "Station development tier increases the chance of finding Galaxy points or Battleship Energy capsules in asteroids during Discovery mode.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["station", "stations", "capsules", "capsule", "asteroid", "asteroids", "discovery"]
  },
  {
    "id": "18",
    "text": "Station development tier changes the station skin and the main-screen background image in GalaxyTap.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["station", "stations", "skin", "tiers", "affects"]
  },
  {
    "id": "19",
    "text": "To earn TON in GalaxyTap, you need to open Galaxy Chests.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["earn", "earn ton", "galaxy chest", "chest", "galaxy chests", "ton", "chest", "chests", "crypto"]
  },
  {
    "id": "20",
    "text": "Battleship development tier affects the damage cap per click of the click power skill and the battleship skin on the main screen.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["battleship", "battleships", "power", "skin", "affects"]
  },
  {
    "id": "21",
    "text": "Players can upgrade battle skills (click power, crit chance, crit power, auto-recovery rate and limit of battleship energy) to boost performance in Battle mode.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["skill", "skills", "upgrade", "crit chance", "crit power", "battle energy", "battleship energy"]
  },
  {
    "id": "22",
    "text": "Click power affects damage per click in Battle mode.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["power", "battle", "click power"]
  },
  {
    "id": "23",
    "text": "Crit chance affects the probability of dealing critical damage on normal clicks in Battle mode.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["crit", "battle", "crit chance"]
  },
  {
    "id": "24",
    "text": "Crit power affects the absolute amount of critical damage dealt by a critical attack in Battle mode.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["crit", "battle", "crit power"]
  },
  {
    "id": "25",
    "text": "The higher the level of battle skills, the more power you have in Battle mode.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["power", "battle", "battle skills"]
  },
  {
    "id": "26",
    "text": "To increase the development tier of your battleship and station, upgrade overall technology and control levels in the Workshop and purchase mission cards.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["station", "stations", "upgrade", "upgrading"]
  },
  {
    "id": "27",
    "text": "To raise the overall technology level in the Workshop, upgrade technology cards to the same level.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["technology", "workshop", "technology level"]
  },
  {
    "id": "28",
    "text": "To raise the overall control level in the Workshop, upgrade control cards to the same level.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["control", "workshop", "control level"]
  },
  {
    "id": "29",
    "text": "The higher the levels of technology and control cards in the Workshop, the more Galaxy points a player can mine.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["technology", "mining", "control", "mining power"]
  },
  {
    "id": "30",
    "text": "Mining works offline for up to 4 hours if auto-mining is disabled, and continues uninterrupted when the player is online.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["automining", "mining", "offline", "online"]
  },
  {
    "id": "31",
    "text": "When the auto-mining function is enabled, mining works non-stop.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["enable", "automining"]
  },
  {
    "id": "32",
    "text": "Auto-mining can be activated for free only if the player has an active Nexus station.",
