    "tags": ["duration", "automining"]
  },
  {
    "id": "35",
    "text": "Auto-mining can be reactivated if it has been turned off.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["disabled", "automining"]
  },
  {
    "id": "36",
    "text": "Enabling auto-mining also activates the auto-clicker in Battle mode and the freeze feature in Discovery mode.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["autoclicker", "automining", "freeze"]
  },
  {
    "id": "37",
    "text": "The freeze feature in Discovery mode stops the rotation of asteroids that hide capsules with Galaxy points and Battleship Energy.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["freeze", "discovery"]
  },
  {
    "id": "38",
    "text": "The auto-clicker in Battle mode remains active as long as auto-mining is active.",
