    "tags": ["battle", "creature", "monsters", "creatures", "monster", "attributes"]
  },
  {
    "id": "45",
    "text": "In Battle mode, the player can clash with 10 alien races, each evolving over 10 stages (from initial form to god-like).",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["battle", "creature", "monsters", "creatures", "monster"]
  },
  {
    "id": "46",
    "text": "For each defeated creature, the player receives Galaxy points, station energy, and chest keys.",
