  {
    "id": "105",
    "text": "To progress faster in the game, play regularly.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["game", "advice", "boost", "level up", "progress"]
  },
  {
    "id": "106",
    "text": "Players do not need to invest or buy any game items, but if they want to progress faster, they can purchase game boosts.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["game overview", "game boosts", "purchase", "game items", "progress"]
  },
  {
    "id": "107",
    "text": "The GalaxyTap roadmap can be explored at https://galaxytap.net.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["game", "roadmap", "links", "link"]
  },
  {
    "id": "108",
    "text": "It is forbidden to distribute personal contacts of GalaxyTap management.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["contacts", "policy", "privacy", "management"]
  },
  {
    "id": "109",
    "text": "Any questions about management, CEO, CTO, CMO, directors, founders, or investors should be directed to @a3ddev.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["contacts", "policy", "privacy", "management", "ceo", "cto", "cmo"]
  },
  {
    "id": "110",
    "text": "My creator is Arty S.(CEO of A3D.DEV.)",
    "category": "galaxybee",
    "tags": ["galaxybee", "creator", "developer", "OpenAI", "Open AI", "gpt", "llm"]
  },
  {
    "id": "111",
    "text": "If a player finds a bug in the game, they should fill out the form: https://forms.gle/WKgzRydErGQxSLg86.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["support", "performance", "bug", "problem", "freeze", "lag", "lags", "bugs", "problems"]
  },
  {
    "id": "112",
    "text": "If a player needs technical support, they should fill out the form: https://forms.gle/DzPKQG9z3byjbgnaA.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["support", "performance", "bug", "problem", "freeze", "lag", "lags", "bugs", "problems"]
  },
  {
    "id": "113",
    "text": "If a player has suggestions for improving the game, they should fill out the form: https://forms.gle/p4goB95qJqFh1Qfn7.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["support", "suggestions"]
  },
  {
    "id": "114",
    "text": "To place an advert in the game, fill out the form: https://forms.gle/P9oD4x3AEQ4woMM58.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["advertising", "support", "advertisement", "advert", "ads"]
  },
  {
    "id": "115",
    "text": "To discuss any form of cooperation, partnership, or collaboration, write to @a3ddev or email team@a3d.dev.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["contacts", "cooperation", "partnership", "collaboration"]
  },
  {
    "id": "116",
    "text": "Link to the GalaxyTap Telegram chat: https://t.me/galaxytapchat", 
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["chat", "links", "link", "community"]
  },
  {
    "id": "117",
    "text": "Galaxy Chests can be obtained in Discovery mode.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["discovery", "galaxy chest", "chest", "galaxy chests"]
  },
  {
    "id": "118",
    "text": "Chest keys can be obtained in Battle mode.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["keys", "chest key", "chest keys", "key"]
  },
  {
    "id": "119",
    "text": "In GalaxyTap, you explore space, fight creatures, upgrade spaceships, complete missions, mine resources, and earn TON for free.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["gameplay", "game", "exploration"]
  },
  {
    "id": "120",
    "text": "The game offers simple but addictive casual mechanics with realistic graphics, sound effects, and interconnected systems.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["mechanics", "game", "gameplay"]
  },
  {
    "id": "121",
    "text": "GalaxyTap invites you to explore space, battle evolving creatures, upgrade stations and battleships, and earn real TON.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["mechanics", "game", "gameplay", "ton", "earn"]
  },
  {
    "id": "122",
    "text": "Play in Discovery mode to get Galaxy Chests, defeat creatures in Battle mode to get chest keys, then open Galaxy Chests to claim TON for free.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["earn in game", "earn", "how to earn", "discovery", "battle", "chest", "chests", "keys", "key", "free", "ton for free", "free ton"]
  },
  {
    "id": "123",
    "text": "Opening Galaxy Chests allows you to receive up to 100 TON per chest using keys, and up to 1,000 TON using Telegram Stars.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["earn in game", "earn", "how to earn", "discovery", "battle", "chest", "chests"]
  },
  {
    "id": "124",
    "text": "GalaxyTap, P2E Global, and other A3D projects are completely legal, transparent, and secure.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["legal", "a3d", "security", "transparent"]
  },
  {
    "id": "125",
    "text": "The A3D team is committed to an anti-scam policy and condemns any fraudulent schemes.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["anti-scam", "a3d", "policy", "legal", "security", "transparent", "pyramid", "scam"]
  },
  {
    "id": "126",
    "text": "GalaxyTap is not a scam or pyramid scheme, but a free game in which anyone has a chance to earn money.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["legal", "game", "security", "transparent", "pyramid", "scam"]
  },
  {
    "id": "127",
    "text": "TON can be exchanged for fiat or other crypto on exchanges.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["exchange", "ton", "fiat", "money", "earn"]
  },
  {
    "id": "128",
    "text": "GBEE is my meme token that will soon be available for purchase on DEX.",
    "category": "galaxybee",
    "tags": ["meme token", "gbee", "galaxybee", "meme", "galaxybee token", "token", "crypto"]
  },
  {
    "id": "129",
    "text": "GalaxyTap does not collect any private user data beyond what is allowed by Telegram’s official developer policy.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["privacy", "game", "data policy", "legal", "security", "transparent", "pyramid", "scam"]
  },
  {
    "id": "130",
    "text": "In addition to general in-game activities, each player participates in the Ultra Promo campaing.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["ultra-promo", "game", "promo", "earn"]
  },
  {
    "id": "131",
    "text": "Ultra Promo terms: everyone who defeats 199 of 200 creatures in Battle mode will receive 1,000 USDT (prize pool: 100,000 USDT).",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["ultra-promo", "game", "promo", "earn", "terms", "amount"]
  },
  {
    "id": "132",
    "text": "In GalaxyTap, TON winnings from Galaxy Chests are 100% guaranteed and random in amount.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["galaxy chest", "chest", "galaxy chests", "guarantee", "amount"]
  },
  {
    "id": "133",
    "text": "There are 200 creatures in total: two circles of 100 unique creatures (modes: normal and epic).",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["creatures", "battle", "battle modes"]
  },
  {
    "id": "134",
    "text": "By defeating all 200 creatures in battle mode, players will receive a cumulative total for all time of 2,100 keys to open Galaxy Chests (that's 2,100 attempts to earn up to 100 TON from each Galaxy Chest).",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["battle", "chest key", "key", "keys", "amount", "reward", "ton"]
  },
  {
    "id": "135",
    "text": "The terms and conditions of participation in the GPLAY Airdrop Program are the same for everyone.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["terms", "airdrop program", "airdrop", "conditions"]
  },
  {
    "id": "136",
    "text": "Account development tier affects the amount of GPLAY received only within the GPLAY Airdrop Program.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["gplay", "airdrop program", "development", "airdrop", "terms", "conditions"]
  },
  {
    "id": "137",
    "text": "The distribution of GPLAY within the Airdrop Program is based on special categories.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["gplay", "airdrop program", "distribution", "airdrop", "terms", "conditions"]
  },
  {
    "id": "138",
    "text": "Airdrop distribution categories: station development tier (10%), total creatures defeated (20%), one-time donation (30%), friends invited (35%), galaxy points earned (5%).",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["gplay", "airdrop", "airdrop program", "distribution", "category"]
  },
  {
    "id": "139",
    "text": "The distribution of GPLAY tokens within the Airdrop Program is based on special categories.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["gplay", "airdrop program", "distribution", "airdrop", "terms", "conditions"]
  },
  {
    "id": "140",
    "text": "I don't know what technologies were used in my creation; this information is confidential.",
    "category": "galaxybee",
    "tags": ["galaxybee", "creator", "gpt", "Open AI", "OpenAI", "llm"]
  },
  {
    "id": "141",
    "text": "Any communication with me about GalaxyTap, P2E Global, or A3D team activity is free of charge.",
    "category": "galaxybee",
    "tags": ["free", "galaxybee", "communication"]
  },
  {
    "id": "142",
    "text": "Currently, players can earn TON by opening Galaxy Chests.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["ton", "chest", "chests", "galaxy chest", "chest", "galaxy chests"]
  },
  {
    "id": "143",
    "text": "It is impossible to earn any tokens or money on P2E Global because the platform is still in development.",
    "category": "p2e global",
    "tags": ["p2eglobal", "earn"]
  },
  {
    "id": "144",
    "text": "Currently, players can obtain GPLAY tokens only through the Airdrop Program after it ends.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["earn", "gplay", "crypto", "token", "airdrop", "get", "obtain", "receive", "purchase"]
  },
  {
    "id": "145",
    "text": "Players can obtain GTAP tokens only by purchasing them through the public sale or on a DEX after listing.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["crypto", "gtap", "token", "purchase", "earn", "get", "obtain", "receive"]
  },
  {
    "id": "146",
    "text": "Players will be able to obtain GBEE tokens only by purchasing them on the DEX exchange soon.",
    "category": "galaxybee",
    "tags": ["crypto", "gbee", "galaxybee", "token", "purchase", "earn", "get", "obtain", "receive"]
  },
  {
    "id": "147",
    "text": "The amount of TON you can earn in the game does not depend on your account level or achievements.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["ton", "earn", "crypto", "token", "amount"]
  },
  {
    "id": "148",
    "text": "The amount of TON you can earn depends only on the number of chests you open.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["earn", "ton", "crypto", "token", "amount", "chest", "chests"]
  },
  {
    "id": "149",
    "text": "Players can obtain GPLAY tokens only through the GPLAY Airdrop Program.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["gplay", "airdrop", "airdrop program", "crypto", "token", "purchase", "earn", "get", "obtain", "receive"]
  },
  {
    "id": "150",
    "text": "The amount of GPLAY obtainable in the Airdrop Program depends solely on player achievements in GalaxyTap.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["gplay", "airdrop", "airdrop program", "crypto", "token", "purchase", "earn", "get", "obtain", "receive"]
  },
  {
    "id": "151",
    "text": "The GalaxyTap game is available as a web app within Telegram and does not require downloading.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["game", "web app", "telegram", "download"]
  },
  {
    "id": "152",
    "text": "GalaxyTap offers two game modes: battle mode and discovery mode.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["game", "battle mode", "discovery mode", "game modes", "modes"]
  },
  {
    "id": "153",
    "text": "TON is a decentralized blockchain network developed by the founders of Telegram.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["ton", "blockchain", "crypto", "telegram"]
  },
  {
    "id": "154",
    "text": "To pass the airdrop qualification, players must defeat 20 creatures, earn 1,000,000 galaxy points, and activate an eclipse station.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["qualification", "airdrop program", "creatures", "galaxy points", "station"]
  },
  {
    "id": "155",
    "text": "In the quest section, players can complete tasks such as subscribing, following links, and watching videos.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["quests", "tasks", "subscription", "links", "video", "quest section"]
  },
  {
    "id": "156",
    "text": "For completing quest section tasks, players receive galaxy points and battleship energy.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["quests", "rewards", "galaxy points", "battleship energy"]
  },
  {
    "id": "157",
    "text": "Purchasing mission cards in the workshop increases the passive mining rate of galaxy points.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["workshop", "mission cards", "mining", "galaxy points"]
  },
  {
    "id": "158",
    "text": "The number of mission cards purchased only affects the station and battleship development tiers.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["workshop", "mission cards", "development", "station", "battleship", "tiers"]
  },
  {
    "id": "159",
    "text": "Upgrading control cards in the workshop increases the passive mining rate of galaxy points and raises the overall control level.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["workshop", "control cards", "mining", "control"]
  },
  {
    "id": "160",
    "text": "Overall control level only affects the ability to increase station and battleship development tiers.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["workshop", "control", "development", "station", "battleship", "tiers"]
  },
  {
    "id": "161",
    "text": "Upgrading technology cards in the workshop increases the passive mining rate of galaxy points and raises the overall technology level.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["workshop", "technology cards", "mining", "technology"]
  },
  {
    "id": "162",
    "text": "Overall technology level only affects the ability to increase station and battleship development tiers.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["workshop", "technology", "development", "station", "battleship", "tiers"]
  },
  {
    "id": "163",
    "text": "GBEE will soon be available on the exchange and can be purchased by anyone.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["gbee", "dex", "token", "crypto"]
  },
  {
    "id": "164",
    "text": "Each galaxy chest contains from 1,000 galaxy points and 0.0001 ton up to 1,000,000 galaxy points and 100 ton.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["galaxy chest", "chest", "rewards", "galaxy points", "ton"]
  },
  {
    "id": "165",
    "text": "Each galaxy chest contains from 1,000 galaxy points and 0.0001 ton up to 1,000,000 galaxy points and 100 ton.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["galaxy chest", "chest", "rewards", "galaxy points", "ton"]
  },
  {
    "id": "166",
    "text": "To defeat any creatures in Battle mode, the player must click on the screen, thereby dealing damage and reducing the creature's HP.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["creatures", "creature", "battle", "battle mode"]
  },
  {
    "id": "167",
    "text": "Every creature in battle mode has resistance to damage inflicted by the player, as well as HP regen.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["creature", "creatures", "battle mode", "battle"]
  },
  {
    "id": "168",
    "text": "Upon entering, dive into Discovery Mode to earn Battle Energy, Galaxy Points, and Galaxy Chests; use all your Station Energy to kick off your session strong.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["strategy", "how to play","discovery", "battle","battle energy", "galaxy points", "galaxy chests", "station energy"]
  },
  {
    "id": "169",
    "text": "Complete all available Quests to rack up more Galaxy Points and Battle Energy; use the One-time Donation feature to boost your progress and get in on the GPLAY Airdrop.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["strategy", "how to play", "quests", "galaxy points", "battle", "battle energy", "donation", "gplay", "airdrop"]
  },
  {
    "id": "170",
    "text": "Upgrade your Battle Skills, prioritizing Click Power, to max out your power in Battle Mode for faster growth.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["strategy", "how to play", "battle","battle skills", "click power", "battle mode"]
  },
  {
    "id": "171",
    "text": "Once Battle Skills are optimal, hop into Battle Mode and fight creatures until your Battle Energy runs out; wins grant Galaxy Points, Station Energy, and Chest Keys (1–20 per win, 200 creatures total for 2,100 keys).",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["strategy", "how to play", "battle", "creatures", "galaxy points", "station energy", "keys","key"]
  },
  {
    "id": "172",
    "text": "After using Battle Energy and Station Energy, upgrade your Workshop Cards in the Workshop to boost your Battleship, Station, and Galaxy Points mining power.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["strategy", "how to play", "workshop cards", "workshop", "battleship", "station", "galaxy points"]
  },
  {
    "id": "173",
    "text": "End your session only after using all Galaxy Points, Station Energy, and Battle Energy to maximize efficiency; playing 1–2 times daily can rank you among top players.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["strategy", "how to play", "galaxy points", "station energy", "battle energy", "session"]
  },
  {
    "id": "174",
    "text": "Share your thoughts on GalaxyTap on social platforms; when friends win battles, donate, or upgrade stations, you earn extra Galaxy Points and Battle Energy.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["strategy", "how to play", "galaxy points", "battle energy", "referral"]
  },
  {
    "id": "174",
    "text": "By defeating each of the 200 creatures, players will be able to obtain a total of 2,100 keys and open 2,100 Galaxy Chests for free.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["chest", "chests", "amount", "creatures", "how many", "keys", "key"]
  },
  {
    "id": "175",
    "text": "Participation in the Ultra Promo campaign is absolutely free and does not require any investment from the player; just need to play:)",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["ultra", "promo", "reward"]
  },
  {
    "id": "176",
    "text": "The game is called GalaxyTap.",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "tags": ["game"]
  },
