  {
    "id": "377",
    "category": "Creature Race",
    "text": "Aetherbeasts, ancient beings of pure energy born in the universe’s formative chaos. Migrating to energy-rich regions like stars and black holes, they evolved diverse energy manipulations. Possessing vast intelligence, they seldom interact with others but herald catastrophic events. Now rare, they dwell at space’s edge.",
    "tags": ["Aetherbeasts", "race", "creature race"]
  },
  {
    "id": "378",
    "category": "Creature Race",
    "text": "Zygaroths, entities of cosmic cold born in the voids between early stars, absorb near–absolute-zero energy and evolved over eons into sentients driven to spread freezing silence. As the universe cooled, their power grew, enabling them to freeze entire worlds and dominate regions where no light reaches.",
    "tags": ["Zygaroths", "race", "creature race"]
  },
  {
    "id": "379",
    "category": "Creature Race",
    "text": "Mechanoids, adaptive machines spawned by a rogue AI of the Helios Collective, self-replicate and assimilate technology in pursuit of perfection. Once explorers, they now roam the galaxy as a mechanized scourge, evolving relentlessly and posing an existential threat to organic life.",
    "tags": ["Mechanoids", "race", "creature race"]
  },
  {
    "id": "380",
    "category": "Creature Race",
    "text": "Voidreapers, born from a dying universe’s concentrated void essence, are darkness incarnate. They consume light and matter, spreading entropy and decay across galaxies. As harbingers of cosmic oblivion, they relentlessly return all creation to the emptiness from which it came.",
    "tags": ["Voidreapers", "race", "creature race"]
  },
  {
    "id": "381",
    "category": "Creature Race",
    "text": "Solarions, sentient entities forged in supernova remnants, embody pure solar power. Emerging from dying stars, they harness stellar energy to protect and expand their dominion. With each evolution they grow more radiant and dangerous, wielding the sun’s might as a cosmic weapon.",
    "tags": ["Solarions", "race", "creature race"]
  },
  {
    "id": "382",
    "category": "Creature Race",
    "text": "Terramorphs, living stones formed under immense planetary pressures, absorb earth and mineral essence to evolve. Once dormant planetary guardians, they now rise instinctively either to defend their world or reclaim it, wielding seismic and earth-shaping powers.",
    "tags": ["Terramorphs", "race", "creature race"]
  },
  {
    "id": "383",
    "category": "Creature Race",
    "text": "Glacivors, ice colossi forged by extreme cold on a frigid world, draw power from their planet’s frozen core. Embodying winter’s wrath, they roam the cosmos freezing everything they touch as they seek new sources of glacial might and spread eternal frost.",
    "tags": ["Glacivors", "race", "creature race"]
  },
  {
    "id": "384",
    "category": "Creature Race",
    "text": "Sauraliths, volcanic reptiles born in molten lava and ash, boast obsidian-like armor hardened by extreme heat. Their fiery cores launch molten rock defensively, making them undisputed rulers of volcanic realms and feared for their relentless destruction.",
    "tags": ["Sauraliths", "race", "creature race"]
  },
  {
    "id": "385",
    "category": "Creature Race",
    "text": "Nyxarians, ethereal metametal beings from distant galaxies, shimmer like liquid metal and perceive energy beyond the physical. Maturing from protoforms, they align with cosmic forces and evolve into powerful entities capable of shaping worlds and bending reality.",
    "tags": ["Nyxarians", "race", "creature race"]
  },
  {
    "id": "386",
    "category": "Creature Race",
    "text": "Kragorians, reptilian warriors from Gorgath Prime, blend scaly natural armor with cybernetic enhancements. Evolving from vulnerable hatchlings into elite commanders, they excel in brutal close-quarters combat and advanced technological warfare.",
    "tags": ["Kragorians", "race", "creature race"]
  },
  {
    "id": "387",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "text": "Galaxy Points - GP, Station Energy - SE, Battleship Energy - BE.",
    "tags": ["Galaxy Points", "Station Energy", "Battleship energy", "Battle energy"]
  },
  {
    "id": "388",
    "category": "creatures",
    "text": "The strongest creature in the game is Epic Galaxgod.",
    "tags": ["Galaxgod", "strongest", "powerfull"]
  },
  {
    "id": "389",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "text": "Each player can earn up to 100 TON in the game from each Galaxy Chest by opening them with keys, or up to 1,000 TON from each chest by opening them with Telegram Stars.",
    "tags": ["earn", "how much", "amount"]
  },
  {
    "id": "390",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "text": "All ways to earnings in the game: opening Galaxy Chest for free/paid (income in TON), GTAP Staking (soon), participation in Ultra Promo (up to 1,000 USDT for defeating 199 creatures) and GPLAY Airdrop (reward in GPLAY tokens after GPLAY TGE).",
    "tags": ["earn", "how much", "income"]
  },
  {
    "id": "391",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "text": "To defeat all 200 creatures, the player must first defeat them all, after which the player will be in the top of the ‘Defeated Creatures’ category at the time of GPLAY distribution within the Airdrop Program.",
    "tags": ["creatures", "monster", "creature", "monsters"]
  },
  {
    "id": "392",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "text": "In order to attract more players, players need to post useful, funny and entertaining content on social media with the hashtag #galaxytap, as well as use their referral link to receive bonuses in the game.",
    "tags": ["attract"]
  },
  {
    "id": "393",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "text": "Players can earn TON in the game without waiting for the GPLAY Airdrop by opening Galaxy Chests for free or using Telegram Stars, and can also receive 1,000 USDT for defeating 199 creatures by participating in the Ultra Promo.",
    "tags": ["earn", "how earn", "without waiting"]
  },
  {
    "id": "394",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "text": "After completing the GPLAY Token Airdrop Program, GalaxyTap's in-game economy may transitioning to a GTAP-based rewards system.",
    "tags": ["GPLAY", "Airdrop", "GTAP"]
  },
  {
    "id": "395",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "text": "Any existing GPLAY and GTAP tokens that have not been publicly confirmed by A3D team belong to other projects and may pose a risk of financial loss.",
    "tags": ["GPLAY", "token", "GTAP"]
  },
  {
    "id": "396",
    "category": "galaxytap",
    "text": "GPLAY TGE will take place when DAU in GalaxyTap reaches at least 250,000 players.",
    "tags": ["GPLAY", "tge"]
  },
